---
import CliRecording from "../components/CliRecording.astro";
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Get Started · Argus"
  description="观看 Argus 的真实运行流程：Manager 回复、角色交接、Engineer 执行、Reviewer 打回与成果交付。"
>
  <section class="page-hero compact product-hero">
    <div class="shell demo-shell">
      <p class="eyebrow">Get started</p>
      <h1>打开 Argus，<em>直接说你要什么。</em></h1>
      <p class="lede">
        下面不是界面截图，而是两段真实运行：Manager 如何组织回复，团队如何接力，Reviewer 为什么打回，以及结果怎样进入你的工作台。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="#cli">看完整 CLI 流程 →</a>
        <a class="button" href="#webui">看 Web 研究轨迹 ↓</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="runtime-flow" aria-label="Argus 运行流程">
    <div class="shell demo-shell">
      <div class="runtime-flow__track">
        <div><span>01</span><strong>用户目标</strong></div>
        <div><span>02</span><strong>Manager 路由</strong></div>
        <div><span>03</span><strong>Planner 拆解</strong></div>
        <div><span>04</span><strong>Engineer 执行</strong></div>
        <div><span>05</span><strong>Reviewer 裁决</strong></div>
        <div><span>06</span><strong>成果交付</strong></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="cli" class="section demo-section">
    <div class="shell demo-shell">
      <div class="demo-intro">
        <div class="section-head">
          <p class="eyebrow">01 · Terminal cockpit</p>
          <h2>先看 Argus 如何回复，再看团队如何接力。</h2>
          <p>用户直接追问执行过程；Manager 显示分类、决策与等待阶段，再按角色给出交接实录，最后在终端中打开 Reviewer 验收过的成品。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="launch-command" aria-label="CLI 启动命令">
          <span>启动</span>
          <code>argus</code>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="demo-frame terminal-demo">
        <div class="demo-frame__bar">
          <span class="window-dots" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i></span>
          <strong>Argus CLI</strong>
          <span>REAL RUN</span>
        </div>
        <CliRecording />
      </div>

      <p class="demo-caption">
        <strong>32 秒真实回放</strong>
        《秋江赋》经历 4 轮协作：Reviewer 连续打回门禁与展示问题，Manager 接手收尾，终审通过后直接预览终稿。
      </p>
      <div class="demo-points" aria-label="CLI 功能">
        <span>阶段化回复</span>
        <span>角色交接实录</span>
        <span>Reviewer 多轮打回</span>
        <span>终稿原地预览</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="webui" class="section surface demo-section">
    <div class="shell demo-shell">
      <div class="demo-intro">
        <div class="section-head">
          <p class="eyebrow">02 · Web cockpit</p>
          <h2>不是任务列表，是一条可以钻取的研究轨迹。</h2>
          <p>搜索进入真实数学任务，先读 Argus 的进度回复，再展开 Engineer 的验证输出与 Reviewer 的裁决；Mission 视图保留全过程回放与证据预览。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="launch-command" aria-label="WebUI 启动命令">
          <span>启动</span>
          <code>argus --web</code>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="demo-frame browser-demo">
        <div class="demo-frame__bar">
          <span class="window-dots" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i></span>
          <strong>Argus WebUI</strong>
          <span>REAL RUN</span>
        </div>
        <video
          data-web-demo
          controls
          loop
          muted
          playsinline
          preload="metadata"
          poster="/assets/demos/argus-web-demo-poster.webp"
          aria-label="Argus WebUI 真实操作演示"
        >
          <source src="/assets/demos/argus-web-demo.webm" type="video/webm" />
          <a href="/assets/demos/argus-web-demo.webm">下载 WebUI 演示视频</a>
        </video>
      </div>

      <p class="demo-caption">
        <strong>28 秒真实回放</strong>
        Erdős–Straus 研究中，两种算法完成 N≤10000 验证后仍被 Reviewer 打回；随后查看 Mission replay、冻结范围证据与已完成成果。
      </p>
      <div class="demo-points" aria-label="WebUI 功能">
        <span>会话搜索</span>
        <span>Agent 对话</span>
        <span>Engineer 原始输出</span>
        <span>Reviewer 裁决</span>
        <span>Mission replay</span>
        <span>证据与结果预览</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="shell demo-shell">
      <div class="cta-band product-cta">
        <p class="eyebrow">Choose your cockpit</p>
        <h2>从一句话，到一条可审查的研究轨迹。</h2>
        <p>终端与浏览器共享同一份对话、角色状态、执行证据与 Reviewer 裁决。没有 Python 交互层，也没有隐藏在演示之外的另一套流程。</p>
        <div class="launch-options">
          <div><span>Terminal</span><code>argus</code></div>
          <div><span>Browser</span><code>argus --web</code></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button" href="https://github.com/lbx154/argus-skill#快速开始">查看安装说明 →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>

<script>
  const video = document.querySelector("[data-web-demo]");

  if (
    video instanceof HTMLVideoElement &&
    !window.matchMedia("(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)").matches
  ) {
    new IntersectionObserver(
      ([entry]) => {
        if (entry?.isIntersecting) void video.play();
        else video.pause();
      },
      { threshold: 0.25 },
    ).observe(video);
  }
</script>
